Key Match Events: Benin come from behind to beat Nigeria 2-1 for dia group C World Cup qualifying match.
Mounni score di winner for Benin afta Dossou bin equalise Nigeria goal wey Onyedike score.
Nigeria dey fifth position wit four points for table, while Benin dey top group C wit seven points.
If di oda teams for di group win dia games Nigeria go dey bottom of di group.
